OL,3,CHospice bosses call on MPs to support
OL,4,Ccalls for better funding
OL,6,FHospice leaders from across Greater
OL,7,FManchester have travelled to London to
OL,8,Fcall for better funding models from
OL,9,Fthe government.
OL,11,FBosses from eight end-of-life care
OL,12,Fcentres made the trip to Westminster,
OL,13,Ffor an event hosted by Makerfield MP
OL,14,FJosh Simons.
OL,16,FSince 2020 hospices in Greater
OL,17,FManchester have seen their total costs
OL,18,Fincrease by 33%, with most of this
OL,19,Fcost having to be met by fundraising
OL,20,Ffrom the local community.
