OL,3,CHospice bosses call on MPs to support
OL,4,Ccalls for better funding
OL,6,FOn Tuesday those who run those
OL,7,Fhospices asked MPs to sign a joint
OL,8,Fletter to the Minister of State for
OL,9,FHealth and Social Care, calling for
OL,10,Fthe government's new 10-year health
OL,11,Fplan to include commitments to
OL,12,Fimproving palliative and end of life
OL,13,Fcare, and reforming the hospice
OL,14,Ffunding model.
OL,16,FKaren Edwards OBE, the Chief Executive
OL,17,Fof Derian House Children's Hospice in
OL,18,FChorley said: "We want their support
OL,19,Fto reform the funding model for
OL,20,Fhospices with a new 10-year health
OL,21,Fplan.
OL,26,@zD@OOU
