OL,3,CHospice bosses call on MPs to support
OL,4,Ccalls for better funding
OL,6,F"Currently #11.7bn is spent on health
OL,7,Fcare for people in the last year of
OL,8,Flife in the UK, but 80% of that
OL,9,Ffunding is spent in hospitals. We
OL,10,Fbelieve this money could be better
OL,11,Fused by investing in hospice care,
OL,12,Fwhich currently only receives 4% of
OL,13,Fthis funding.
OL,15,F"We are forever grateful for our
OL,16,Fcommunity for doing so much to support
OL,17,FDerian House Children's Hospice, but
OL,18,Fwe shouldn't have to depends on our
OL,19,Fsupporters as much as we do to fund
OL,20,Fthese essential services for children."
