OL,3,CHospice bosses call on MPs to support
OL,4,Ccalls for better funding
OL,6,FThe group posed for pictures outside
OL,7,Fthe Houses of Parliament before
OL,8,Fmeeting with Makerfield MP Josh
OL,9,FSimons, who sponsored the event.
OL,11,FMr Simons, who's represented
OL,12,FMakerfield since last July, said: "The
OL,13,Fgovernment has already delivered
OL,14,Frecord funding, #100 million pounds
OL,15,Facross the country. Today we'll be
OL,16,Fmaking the case for a longer term
OL,17,Fsustainable funding solution to
OL,18,Fsupport hospices and end-of-life care."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
