OL,3,CHospice bosses call on MPs to support
OL,4,Ccalls for better funding
OL,6,F"So often they can't actually access
OL,7,Fthat capital investment they did need
OL,8,Fto fix underlying problems. So the
OL,9,F#100 million, that's to fix those
OL,10,Funderlying capital problems with
OL,11,Fbuildings and machines. That will set
OL,12,Four hospice sector off on a new
OL,13,Ffooting going forward."
