OL,3,CHospice bosses call on MPs to support
OL,4,Ccalls for better funding
OL,6,FAsked if the funding system is
OL,7,Ffundamentally broken, the Labour MP
OL,8,Fsaid: "We need to shift our entire
OL,9,Fhealth system away from acute hospital
OL,10,Fdriven care, which is where all the
OL,11,Ffunding and all the focus goes,
OL,12,Ftowards community healthcare,
OL,13,Fdelivered in the place where people
OL,14,Flive."
OL,16,FLeigh Vallance, the Chief Executive at
OL,17,FBolton Hospice said she wanted to
OL,18,Fbring 'their story' to parliament.
