OL,3,CHospice bosses call on MPs to support
OL,4,Ccalls for better funding
OL,6,FShe said: "We wanted to bring our
OL,7,Fstory to parliament to speak directly
OL,8,Fto our MPs just about the added value
OL,9,Fthat hospices bring both to the NHS
OL,10,Fand the wider community.
OL,12,F"Parliament is in danger of seeing
OL,13,Fhospices shrink at the very time when
OL,14,Fthey need to see us stablise or expand.
