OL,3,CHospice bosses call on MPs to support
OL,4,Ccalls for better funding
OL,6,F"Our funding from the Government has
OL,7,Freduced gradually over the last 15
OL,8,Fyears. In the meantime our costs have
OL,9,Fincreased and there's only so much
OL,10,Fthat local communities can do to raise
OL,11,Fthe funds to fill that gap. I think
OL,12,Fit's only fair and reasonable that
OL,13,Fpeople within our communities who
OL,14,Fraise over 70 per cent of our funding
OL,15,Fcan get a fair deal from our
OL,16,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
