OL,3,CHospice bosses call on MPs to support
OL,4,Ccalls for better funding
OL,6,FKaren Edwards, who runs Derian House,
OL,7,Fsaid:"By investing in hospice care, we
OL,8,Fcan reduce hospice admissions and make
OL,9,Fit more likely that people can die in
OL,10,Ftheir place of choosing. It is better
OL,11,Ffor people, their families and the
OL,12,FNHS."
OL,14,FRepresentatives from Derian House,
OL,15,FBolton Hospice, Bury Hospice, Dr
OL,16,FKershaw's, Springhill Hospice, St
OL,17,FAnn's Hospice, Wigan & Leigh Hospice
OL,18,Fand Willow Wood Hospice all attended
OL,19,Fthe event in London.
